02:34:33,540 --> 02:34:38,720
Yes... yes. It was from that day on

1270
02:34:39,890 --> 02:34:40,680
What's mean?

1271
02:34:42,430 --> 02:34:43,810
I've killed him

1272
02:34:54,320 --> 02:34:55,610
I won't desert you.

1273
02:34:56,620 --> 02:34:59,200
